                ]]>
            </summary>
        <content type="html">
            <![CDATA[
                <p>We packed up on Saturday and headed out Sunday morning from Ottawa - a beautiful morning.  We listened to the Breaking of Bread from Ottawa enroute.  Amy drove a good part of the way.</p>
<figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3//IMG_0152.jpg" sizes="100vw" srcset="https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3//responsive/IMG_0152-xs.jpg 300w ,https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3//responsive/IMG_0152-sm.jpg 480w ,https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3//responsive/IMG_0152-md.jpg 768w ,https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3//responsive/IMG_0152-lg.jpg 1024w ,https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3//responsive/IMG_0152-xl.jpg 1360w ,https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3//responsive/IMG_0152-2xl.jpg 1600w"  alt="" width="4032" height="3024"></figure>
<p>We stopped in Mattawa for lunch at a pretty little rest area - the same place that Amy and I stopped last year.  We had brought stuff for lunch, so had croissants with ham and tomates and macaroni salad, with tea.  It was such a clear blue sky, just a few clouds.</p>
<figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3//IMG_0155-2.jpg" sizes="100vw" srcset="https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3//responsive/IMG_0155-2-xs.jpg 300w ,https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3//responsive/IMG_0155-2-sm.jpg 480w ,https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3//responsive/IMG_0155-2-md.jpg 768w ,https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3//responsive/IMG_0155-2-lg.jpg 1024w ,https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3//responsive/IMG_0155-2-xl.jpg 1360w ,https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3//responsive/IMG_0155-2-2xl.jpg 1600w"  alt="" width="4032" height="3024"></figure>
<p>We headed on, stopping at Tim's in Sudbury, and then for gas in Blind River.  I drove from Sudbury onwards, and we arrived at the Sault around 7pm.  We checked into our hotel and then headed for Giovanni's for supper based on Bruce's recommendation - it was very good!</p>
<figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3//IMG_0159.jpg" sizes="100vw" srcset="https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3//responsive/IMG_0159-xs.jpg 300w ,https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3//responsive/IMG_0159-sm.jpg 480w ,https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3//responsive/IMG_0159-md.jpg 768w ,https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3//responsive/IMG_0159-lg.jpg 1024w ,https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3//responsive/IMG_0159-xl.jpg 1360w ,https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3//responsive/IMG_0159-2xl.jpg 1600w"  alt="" width="4032" height="3024"></figure>
<p>Back to the hotel, then Janet and I headed out to walk down to where her grandmother lived on Woodward Avenue.  Janet spent her summers during high school here helping her grandma run the bookstore - Scripture Gift and Book.  We saw the old hospital where Janet was born, seeminly abandoned now, a sad sight.</p>
<figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3/IMG_0161-3.jpg" sizes="100vw" srcset="https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/IMG_0161-3-xs.jpg 300w ,https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/IMG_0161-3-sm.jpg 480w ,https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/IMG_0161-3-md.jpg 768w ,https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/IMG_0161-3-lg.jpg 1024w ,https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/IMG_0161-3-xl.jpg 1360w ,https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/IMG_0161-3-2xl.jpg 1600w"  alt="" width="4032" height="3024"></figure>
<p>We walked on to grandma's house at 126 Woodward - it hasn't changed too much.</p>
<figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3/EED26497-FFA1-46B4-B68B-0DBFD3E64C7F.jpg" sizes="100vw" srcset="https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/EED26497-FFA1-46B4-B68B-0DBFD3E64C7F-xs.jpg 300w ,https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/EED26497-FFA1-46B4-B68B-0DBFD3E64C7F-sm.jpg 480w ,https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/EED26497-FFA1-46B4-B68B-0DBFD3E64C7F-md.jpg 768w ,https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/EED26497-FFA1-46B4-B68B-0DBFD3E64C7F-lg.jpg 1024w ,https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/EED26497-FFA1-46B4-B68B-0DBFD3E64C7F-xl.jpg 1360w ,https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/EED26497-FFA1-46B4-B68B-0DBFD3E64C7F-2xl.jpg 1600w"  alt="" width="3840" height="2160"></figure>
<p>Then we walked to Scripture Gift and Book Shop, a walk Janet and her grandma made every day during those summers.  The book shop is still going after all these years!</p>
<figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3/048CB434-01AD-4DEC-9D28-05C16DFD0B00.jpg" sizes="100vw" srcset="https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/048CB434-01AD-4DEC-9D28-05C16DFD0B00-xs.jpg 300w ,https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/048CB434-01AD-4DEC-9D28-05C16DFD0B00-sm.jpg 480w ,https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/048CB434-01AD-4DEC-9D28-05C16DFD0B00-md.jpg 768w ,https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/048CB434-01AD-4DEC-9D28-05C16DFD0B00-lg.jpg 1024w ,https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/048CB434-01AD-4DEC-9D28-05C16DFD0B00-xl.jpg 1360w ,https://kkember.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/048CB434-01AD-4DEC-9D28-05C16DFD0B00-2xl.jpg 1600w"  alt="" width="3840" height="2160"></figure>
<p>Still light out even at 10 pm!  Back to our hotel and to bed after a very full day.</p>
